text: Sangaris octomaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1902. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Sangaris octomaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1902
title: Sangaris octomaculata
